oint of water. At 0.175 AU, only scenarios with CO2\nconcentrations of 5% and 95% were found to be habitable. Hence, an additional\nSuper-Earth planet in the GL 581 system in the previously determined dynamical\nstability range would be considered a potentially habitable planet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2011 14:16:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
